e physics of\nthe imaged sample. Because our model accounts for mixed-material voxels\nstemming from blurring inherent to the imaging technique, we reduce the errors\nthat other methods can create at interfaces between materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Sep 2020 16:55:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jan 2021 21:08:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
