of the latter (on\ngrains) at late times and low temperatures, when CS abundances are depressed.\nThis reduces the thioformamide-to-formamide ratio, because the HCS radical is\nnot as readily available under these conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Sep 2020 10:34:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-08"}
