e $v$ of good reduction co-prime to $d$ . This is an analogue of the\nMordell-Lang conjecture on finite rank groups for polynomial dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Sep 2020 11:35:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 08:14:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 15:06:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-16"}
